snippet.title: Vikavoltius -- Pokémon SHMUP Fangame Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the game here: https://heatphoenix.itch.io/vikavoltius
Join our discord: http://discord.heatphoenix.net/

Vikavoltius -- My Pokémon Shoot 'Em Up game, where you blast enemy Pokémon and bosses for the highest score is now available for download! Go for the highest score!

Featuring:
* Lots of Pokémon!
* 2-player co-op!
* A remixed soundtrack!

Featuring music by Vert-Hex and art by Shenaniganza!
